{"tid":219363,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"搵左兩日求巴絲打搵條片","createTime":"2017-04-27T07:24:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-27T23:51:19.000Z","uid":17884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"07aae19808778cb04467a50e6664449ef7cfeeb5","tid":219363,"uid":17884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T07:24:27.000Z","msg":"話說早兩個月左右係FACEBOOK睇左條片，條片既內容係講課室入邊既特殊學習需要<br />\n片入面係D細路仔既自白，內容係講自閉症兒童上堂訓覺因為佢覺得太簡單，同埋佢一定要做一D野佢先可以聽老師講書<br />\n同埋有講ADHD學生，如果要佢好乖咁座係度佢會好辛苦，要被佢郁，佢郁唔代表佢冇留心老師內容<br />\n<br />\n有冇巴絲打可以幫手搵番條片出來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n初初係FACEBOOK睇完搵唔番，有冇人可以搵番條LINK，麻煩各位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87deb08a60238387ca7ad36edbf300b9ff379dfc","tid":219363,"uid":100442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T07:35:24.000Z","msg":"我想食雪糕"},{"pid":"1d954f063a3c0f51fdaab699353e95cae064e6e5","tid":219363,"uid":17884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T07:44:29.000Z","msg":"有冇人有印象睇過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3abd775638236cb91948625a1369feafa776f33a","tid":219363,"uid":17884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T07:52:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d19e641c738ba8dd5469bd322fdc0fdcc5108991","tid":219363,"uid":17884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T07:58:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cr